Check access to SIANE data

Source: R/esp_check_access.R
esp_check_access.Rd

Check if R has access to resources at https://github.com/rOpenSpain/mapSpain/tree/sianedata.

Usage

esp_check_access()

Value

a logical.

See also

giscoR::gisco_check_access()

Other helper: esp_move_can()

Examples


esp_check_access()
#> [1] TRUE

About rOpenSpain

rOpenSpain is a community of R enthusiasts whose ultimate goal is to create high-quality R packages for data mining public Spanish open sources.
